{"image_id": "ADS_2009_page_218", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "ALLIANCE DATA SYSTEMS CORPORATION", "bbox": [392.8, 140.2, 832.8, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [273.2, 177.7, 952.4, 198.5]}, {"text": "on an unsecured basis. Cardholders reside throughout the United States and are not significantly concentrated in", "bbox": [137.6, 227.9, 1073.4, 248.8]}, {"text": "any one area.", "bbox": [137.6, 252.9, 248.1, 273.8]}, {"text": "Holders of credit cards issued by the Company have available lines of credit, which vary by cardholders that", "bbox": [179.2, 306.2, 1084.8, 327.0]}, {"text": "can be used for purchases of merchandise offered for sale by clients of the Company. These lines of credit", "bbox": [137.6, 331.2, 1024.0, 352.0]}, {"text": "represent elements of risk in excess of the amount recognized in the financial statements. The lines of credit are", "bbox": [137.6, 356.2, 1069.7, 377.0]}, {"text": "subject to change or cancellation by the Company. As of December 31, 2009, the Company had approximately", "bbox": [137.6, 381.2, 1062.9, 402.0]}, {"text": "26.6 million cardholders, having unused lines of credit averaging $1,088 per account.", "bbox": [137.6, 406.2, 851.2, 427.0]}, {"text": "Legal Proceedings", "bbox": [137.6, 473.3, 300.2, 494.1]}, {"text": "From time to time the Company is involved in various claims and lawsuits arising in the ordinary course of", "bbox": [179.2, 512.6, 1074.8, 533.4]}, {"text": "business that it believes will not have a material adverse affect on its business or financial condition, including", "bbox": [137.6, 537.6, 1061.0, 558.4]}, {"text": "claims and lawsuits alleging breaches of the Company’s contractual obligations.", "bbox": [137.6, 562.6, 807.8, 583.4]}, {"text": "18. FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS", "bbox": [137.6, 629.7, 444.7, 650.6]}, {"text": "In accordance with FASB ASC 825, “Financial Instruments,” the Company is required to disclose the fair", "bbox": [179.2, 669.0, 1063.1, 689.8]}, {"text": "value of financial instruments for which it is practical to estimate fair value. To obtain fair values, observable", "bbox": [137.6, 694.0, 1051.2, 714.8]}, {"text": "market prices are used if available. In some instances, observable market prices are not readily available and fair", "bbox": [137.6, 719.0, 1077.8, 739.9]}, {"text": "value is determined using present value or other techniques appropriate for a particular financial instrument.", "bbox": [137.6, 744.0, 1040.6, 764.9]}, {"text": "These techniques involve judgment and as a result are not necessarily indicative of the amounts the Company", "bbox": [137.6, 769.0, 1052.6, 789.9]}, {"text": "would realize in a current market exchange. The use of different assumptions or estimation techniques may have", "bbox": [137.6, 794.0, 1077.6, 814.9]}, {"text": "a material effect on the estimated fair value amounts.", "bbox": [137.6, 819.0, 581.4, 839.9]}, {"text": "Fair Value of Financial Instruments—The estimated fair values of the Company’s financial instruments", "bbox": [179.2, 872.1, 1048.9, 893.1]}, {"text": "were as follows:", "bbox": [137.6, 897.3, 274.2, 918.1]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [820.4, 945.2, 917.7, 961.9]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [737.8, 970.2, 771.1, 986.9]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [967.1, 970.2, 1000.4, 986.9]}, {"text": "Carrying", "bbox": [664.2, 995.2, 730.0, 1011.9]}, {"text": "Amount", "bbox": [668.0, 1011.9, 726.3, 1028.6]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [796.5, 995.2, 827.0, 1011.9]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [790.9, 1011.9, 832.6, 1028.6]}, {"text": "Carrying", "bbox": [893.5, 995.2, 959.2, 1011.9]}, {"text": "Amount", "bbox": [897.2, 1011.9, 955.6, 1028.6]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [1025.7, 995.2, 1056.3, 1011.9]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1020.2, 1011.9, 1061.9, 1028.6]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [817.5, 1036.9, 920.8, 1053.6]}, {"text": "Financial assets", "bbox": [137.6, 1058.7, 277.2, 1079.5]}, {"text": "Cash and cash equi